texts.text: I didn't realize Gakuto was working in parallel.
We're talking about Shionyan's new stage outfit!
As her fan, there was no way I was going to let this theft slide.
But we still have no proof it was stolen...
Is it really a problem if it's gone?
As cute as it might be, they're still just clothes, right?
Humans have so much clothes to begin with too...
It's special.
An idol's stage outfit is like a warrior's suit of armor...
Suit of armor...?
Yeah!
Only the chosen few can stand on that stage and bask in the spotlight.
And the pressure to perform to unbelievable.
A normal girl wearing normal clothes can't possibly stand up there, right?
It's impossible! The stage can consume you at will.
But! Idols are just girls.
Meaning! Their stage outfits are...!
A way for regular girls to stand on the stage, maintain the spotlight,
and kick ass on the battlefield by weaponizing their looks!
Oh... Okay...
Am I right?! Shionyan!!
Hm? Sorry, what?
Shionyan?!
I stopped listening after "the chosen few".
Keep your idol talk between other idol nerds.

*Wince*
Thank you, ma'am...!
Anyways, you said you found Kabuso?
Oh, yeah.
This way. Try to stay hidden just in case.
Oh, you're so strong!
Yes, you're just glowing with power!
Oh? Of course I am...!
Even a Dx2 wouldn't stand a chance against me!
Haha, you're so awesome!
Heh, enough already!
Yikes... He looks strong...
I've got a bad feeling about this...!
That big one...
I see... He got caught by that thing.
His will to survive is pretty strong,
so I wouldn't put it past him to butter up to them and become their flunkey.
Huh?
Wait, have you forgotten?
He's so weak that he can't even take on a run of the mill feral demon.
Come to think of it, the last time he got caught up in something like this...
He was almost eaten by a feral demon...
Exactly. If we don't hurry, it'll be too late.
Hey, S-Shionyan?!
She's gone... Screw it, we're going loud!
Hey, tentacle head!
What? Who the hell do you think you are?!
You really must have a death wish to call me that...!!!
Wait, I know her...!
They're those demon hunters... The Liberators!
Demon hunters...
Let the hunt begin!
Is that how the other demons see us...?
*Whimper*
We're sick of your shenanigans...
Don't come closer! The big man will save us!
What?!
You can do it! I'm sure you can!
Y-yeah! For real?!
There's an ugly ass cat demon hanging around with you, right?
Tell us where he is. Now!
Uhhh...
What's the matter?! Hurry up and get 'em!
Do you really have any use for a pathetic minion like that?
Or do you need to be shown who's really boss?
Nooooo...!
Shionyan, that's not...
I'm sorry...!!
>The demon puts all of his hands together and bows before Shionyan.
What?
I tried to stop you...
That's Kabuso...
Wait what?!
The demons that were being harassed by ex-Acolytes
were saved by you?
He saved us.
Yeah. I was selling tickets like always and came across them.
At first, I thought there was nothing I could do,
but they were really in trouble.
I took a gamble and tried transforming into a strong demon like before.
So they got scared and ran off.
And these guys started praising me so much.
It felt so good that... Well, it's been a while now...
I guess you're more used to being scolded than praised.
You know you're weak, but picked a fight with a Dx2 anyways?
Y-yeah...
That was pretty clever... For someone like you...
W-what?!
Did the salty boss lady just praise me...?!
Congratulations.
She was worried about you.
This makes up for everything that's happened so far...!
Good for you, Kabuso.
N-no, I wasn't...
B-boss! I'll work even harder from now on!
Yeah, okay. I get it.
Wait, hold up. Kabuso, do you know where Shionyan's new outfit is?
She's making a new outfit?! It's not like she has any new songs or...
Excuse me?
No, I have no idea! But I'm looking forward to seeing it...!
So my gun and Vagit's catalyst are...
No clue!
So that means... We're down to our last suspect.
Yes. We need to find Jack the Ripper.
Kabuso, come.
Well, I guess I'm going back with her then.
I feel bad for tricking you guys too.
Don't worry about it! You're still the one that saves us!
Yeah, you're still the big man to us!
Thanks...!
So...
We want to help out too!
The more the merrier.
They really like you.
It's like that story about raiding an island of ogres.
Too many cooks...
You're making me blush...!
But we have a slight problem.
We have no idea where Jack the Ripper went.
Vagit, is it possible for you to track him down?
That may be difficult. I don't really know him so...
I haven't really felt his presence anywhere either...
I see... Then...
>Rika suddenly dashes away.
>*Crash*
>A sawblade now protrudes from where Rika was standing.
*Shriek*
This blade... It has a note attached to it.
Like a letter tied to an arrow...
Huh...?
Everyone, I know where we need to go next.
We just need to follow this map!
